name: Scooter’s Roller Palace
location: 2105 Royal Windsor Dr, Mississauga, ON L5J 1K5 (https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=2105+Royal+Windsor+Dr%2C+Mississauga%2C+ON+L5J+1K5)
description:
-Everyone must pay the entry fee of 16$
-Skate rentals go up to size 15 adult and blades go to size 7 both are 5$ (they don’t supply any other gear)
-You may bring water in a sealed container 
-They take card and cash for entry fee
-Only CASH is accepted for concessions 
-If they ask us or you to do something please comply
-There is small storage locks which need coins to use

This will be during their family friendly times, So no kink gear or any of the sorts

I (@Aqua_Manokit) (https://t.me/Aqua_Manokit) will be there around 1:00pm EST or 13:00 EST
They close around 5:00pm EST or 17:00 EST

The location is by Clarkson GO station 

Recommend NOT to wear a fullsuit, or if you do please wear something appropriate underneath as if asked to take it off you would be in your normal dress. there are kids there, so watch your language and the sorts. You are NOT allowed to have a suit head on the rink, tails and paws are fine, as long as the tail doesn't stick out a lot or drag on the floor.

Feel free to invite friend and family 

Please remember everything you brought as well, along with cleaning up after yourself
